<plot>During the beginning stage of love, most couples wear magical pink glasses. When they are wearing pink glasses, they can love and care for one another peacefully and gently, however, when they take them off, they often fall out of love. This is a Romance/Comedy that describes the changes in a couple's relationship while they wear pink glasses.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?433296</url></doc>
